d Plexus utilities. The reported failure is caused by API changes from 1.9.1 to 2.0.0, not missing external setup.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Upstream tests add optional parser modules such as doxia-module-apt, doxia-module-xdoc, and doxia-module-fml for their own format-specific coverage; generated tests should avoid depending on those formats unless they intentionally add matching test dependencies.\",\n    \"Tests copied from the 1.9.1 scaffold will not compile because classes and methods such as RenderingContext, SkinResourceLoader, enableLogging, and setUsingDefaultTemplate changed or disappeared in 2.0.0.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f4fde8881b9f3ab016a40117708088197bf1f01eb8ba6f202\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 43308, "output": 858, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 44166, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782583660830, "responseId": "resp_0f4fde8881b9f3ab016a40116d611c8197bb22483604d100e8"}, "toolResults": []}
